{% comment %} global changes notes

1. Add | divided_by: 10.0 to all letter-spacing values to convert from percentage to em in theme.liquid and base.css.
2. set font size of heading tags(h1 to h6) in base.css to use rem units instead of px.
3. Remove * 0.1 from letter-spacing calculation in base.css.
4 Add global.css file and move all global changes to this file.
5. Add global.css file to theme.liquid after base.css.
6. Add custom_fonts setting to settings_schema.json to enable/disable custom fonts.
7. Change scale values in settings_schema.json to 100% for all text elements.

